              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": {
                "text": "To accompany our exhibition of the same name, This is a Voice explores the elusive nature of the human voice, with an introduction by Steven Connor and a foreword by Cerys Matthews.",
                "spans": [
                  {
                    "start": 0,
                    "end": 46,
